      <title>交易员等待 ISM 数据提供经济线索，美国国债上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/treasuries-gain-as-traders-wait-for-clues-on-economy-in-ism-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国制造业数据公布前，美国国债收益率上涨，基准收益率降至近一周以来的最低水平，该数据将为美联储今年可能降息幅度提供最新线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/treasuries-gain-as-traders-wait-for-clues-on-economy-in-ism-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:17:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯石油公司找到有争议的货物转运新地点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-oil-finds-a-new-place-to-switch-in-the-mediterranean-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在希腊海军的压力下，俄罗斯石油贸易商在地中海找到了新的原油货物转运地点，这表明打击这一令监管机构和欧洲政府都感到震惊的活动将有多么困难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/russian-oil-finds-a-new-place-to-switch-in-the-mediterranean-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
